Resource Profile: openIMIS Patient

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-patient Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISPatient

Defines a Patient for openIMIS which maps to an Insuree

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: openIMIS Claim Response, openIMIS Claim, openIMIS CommunicationRequest, openIMIS Communication... Show 5 more, openIMIS Contract, openIMIS CoverageEligibilityRequest, openIMIS CoverageEligibilityResponse, openIMIS Coverage and openIMIS Group
  • Examples for this Profile: Patient/jane-doe and Patient/john-doe
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
